                <li>Bundle adds GBP and social ($167/mo)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Where it falls short</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Not pay-per-post — pricing is monthly cadence</li>
                <li>No real-time editor for founders who like writing</li>
                <li>Premium for sub-4-posts-per-month volume</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Founders who want SEO content shipped without hiring or editing.</div>
