            <div><h5>Where it falls short</h5><ul class="no-list"><li>No SEO scoring or schema</li><li>Manual publish step</li><li>Generic image options</li></ul></div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot"><div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Pre-seed founders testing AI writing.</div><a href="/demo/" class="tool-cta-btn">Compare to theStacc &rarr;</a></div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">04</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info"><div class="tool-card-name">Byword</div><div class="tool-card-tag">For Startups That Scale Fast</div></div>
            <div class="tool-card-price"><span class="price">$99/mo</span><span class="per">Starter</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div><h5>What it does well</h5><ul class="yes-list"><li>Bulk programmatic publishing</li><li>WordPress / Webflow / Ghost connectors</li><li>Strong on keyword-list imports</li></ul></div>
            <div><h5>Where it falls short</h5><ul class="no-list"><li>Output reads templated at high volume</li><li>Less suited to brand-voice content</li><li>Pricing scales with article volume</li></ul></div>
          </div>
